results.name: Air Max 2090 SE GS 'Pure Platinum Arctic Punch'
results.colorway: Pure Platinum/Light Liquid Lime/Smoke Grey/Arctic Punch

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Low TD 'Butterfly'
Nike Air Max 1 Evolution Of Icons
results.story: Launching as part of the brand’s 2021 Air Max Day festivities, the Nike Air Max 1 ‘Evolution of Icons’ features a unique design that incorporates familiar details from different Air Max models. The sneaker wears a white leather upper with mismatched Swooshes drawn from the likes of the ‘Neon’ Air Max 95 and ‘Dusty Cactus’ Air Max 93. Molded eyelets are taken from the 90, toe box embroidery references the ‘98, and a gradient grey mudguard offers a further nod to the 95. ‘3.26,’ aka Air Max Day, is debossed on the left heel, while the insole’s timeline graphic depicts the various silhouettes that make up the shoe’s hybrid composition.

results.name: adidas Samba Wales Bonner Collegiate Navy
Wmns Air Max Bella TR 4 'Summit White Orange Pearl'
Force Trout 7 Keystone 'White Light Smoke Grey'
Nike Air Force 1 Low 07 White Game Royal
React Gato 'Grey Fog Bright Crimson'
results.story: The Nike React Gato ‘Grey Fog Bright Crimson’ showcases vibrant accents on an indoor soccer shoe that offers game-ready control and responsiveness. The grey Flyknit upper is fused and molded with a durable compound for improved touch, while a reinforced band around the toe provides added durability. The low-profile silhouette rides on a full-length Nike React midsole, supported by a marbled red rubber outsole fitted with circular pods for enhanced feel.

results.name: Scuderia Ferrari x RCT Xetic Forza 'Rosso Corsa'
adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Kyanite
results.story: The adidas Yeezy 700 V3 ‘Kyanite’ showcases flowing stripes of blue coloring throughout the breathable upper, constructed from monofilament engineered mesh with exoskeletal RPU overlays coated in a glow-in-the-dark finish. Interior bootie construction delivers a snug fit, while a reinforced rubber toe cap provides added durability. The sneaker rides on a lightweight EVA midsole encapsulated in an off-white PU cage, supported by a herringbone rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns FuelCell Propel RMX Wide 'Black Tidepool'
Air Jordan 12 Retro PS 'Arctic Pink'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Air Jordan 12 Retro PS ‘Arctic Pink’ delivers a refreshed take on the classic silhouette that Michael Jordan wore when he captured his fifth NBA title. In addition to the non-traditional palette, the stitched upper is treated to a distressed finish, featuring textured pink remnants that create an abstract pattern on a light grey backdrop. A more intense shade of pink lands on the sneaker’s collar lining, pull tab and branding elements, which include an embroidered Jumpman atop the tongue.

results.name: Helly Hansen x Mirage Tech 'Black Neon'
results.story: Crafted in partnership with the Norwegian outdoor apparel brand, the Helly Hansen x PUMA Mirage Tech ‘Black Neon’ showcases Day-Glo accents on a retro-inspired silhouette that takes its cues from marine patrol gear. The upper is constructed from black nylon with tonal suede overlays and a fluorescent yellow webbing strap integrated into the laces. Dual PUMA and Helly Hansen branding decorates the stitched tongue tag and heel tab. A compression-molded EVA midsole offers lightweight cushioning with each step.

results.name: Nike Air Max 97 Swarovski Polar Blue (W)
results.story: The Swarovski x Nike women’s Air Max 97 ‘Polar Blue’ offers a luxe take on an OG colorway of the retro runner. The sneaker makes use of a silver mesh upper with fused overlays encrusted with tiny Swarovski crystals, adding shimmer to the sneaker’s water ripple-inspired lines. A pale blue mini-Swoosh adorns the lateral quarter panel and oval tongue patch. Buoyant cushioning arrives via a polyurethane midsole, fitted with a historic full-length Max Air unit.

results.name: Ballaholic x Gel Quantum 180 'Cream Metropolis'
results.story: Designed in partnership with the streetball-obsessed Japanese label, the Ballaholic x ASICS Gel Quantum 180 ‘Cream Metropolis’ delivers a lifestyle runner that combines vibrant hues with a smooth, cushioned ride. An off-white textile upper is reinforced with contrasting blue no-sew skins and charcoal suede overlays at the toe and heel, the latter stamped with Ballaholic branding on the lateral side. The cream-colored foam midsole is fortified with 180 degrees of visible Gel cushioning.

results.name: Anderson Bluu x N9002 'Wine Collection - Cabernet'
results.story: Dropping exclusively at Footaction as part of the two-piece ‘Wine Collection’ with the New York-based graphic designer, the Anderson Bluu x Diadora N9002 ‘Cabernet’ takes inspiration from the art of winemaking. The lifestyle runner wears a premium suede upper in varying shades of blue, inspired by the eponymous grapes used in the production of cabernet wine. An embroidered grape graphic adorns the lateral heel of the right shoe, while Anderson’s personal logo appears on the left shoe (reflecting the artist’s left-handedness). A genuine cork insole is the finishing touch.

results.name: Air Zoom Terra Kiger 7 'Black Pure Platinum'
results.story: The Nike Air Zoom Terra Kiger 7 ‘Black Pure Platinum’ highlights neutral tones on a running shoe built to handle rugged terrain. Breathable black mesh is utilized on the upper, featuring synthetic no-sew overlays and a Dynamic Fit System for midfoot lockdown. The Nike React midsole houses an encapsulated Zoom Air unit in the forefoot for extra-responsive cushioning. Underfoot, the rubber outsole is equipped multidirectional traction lugs for superior grip.

results.name: Anderson Bluu x Maverick 'Wine Collection - Chardonnay'
results.story: Conceived in partnership with the self-taught graphic designer, the Anderson Bluu x Diadora Maverick ‘Chardonnay’ is taken from the two-piece ‘Wine Collection,’ released exclusively at Footaction and inspired by the winemaking process. This pair features a premium suede upper in a pastel green hue, redolent of the green-skinned grapes used to create Chardonnay wine. Unique details include a grape graphic embroidered on the heel and genuine cork insoles stamped with Anderson Bluu’s personal logo.

results.name: Chron Solarsoft SB 'Light Smoke Grey Gum'
results.colorway: Light Smoke Grey/Light Smoke Grey/Gum Light Brown/White

results.name: Heritage Vulc SB 'Coast Psychic Blue'
results.story: The Nike Heritage Vulc SB ‘Coast Psychic Blue’ highlights two shades of blue on a streamlined skate shoe crafted from suede with washed canvas quarter panels. A Nike wordmark is embroidered in white lettering on the heel tab, matched by signature Swoosh branding in white leather. A retro exposed-foam tongue combines with a cushy sockliner for a comfortable fit. A gum rubber cupsole anchors the low-profile silhouette.

results.name: Maison Margiela x Club C 'White'
results.story: The Maison Margiela x Reebok Club C ‘White’ takes inspiration from the trompe-l’oeil designs featured in the French fashion house’s Spring/Summer 1996 ready-to-wear collection. The ‘80s trainer carries a monochromatic white upper crafted from a single piece of flat leather, its outer surface printed with a scanned image of an OG Club C. A terry cloth lining and rubber cupsole maintain the sneaker’s original design DNA, while signature Margiela details take the form of stitched detailing on the heel tab and a grid-like arrangement of numbers on the tongue tag.

results.name: PSNY x 327 'We Need Leaders'
results.story: Created in partnership with the fashion label founded by Dao-Yi Chow and Maxwell Osborne, the PSNY x New Balance 327 ‘We Need Leaders’ features a New York-centric design approach. The Yankees’ signature navy blue is applied to the textile and suede upper, while contrasting bright green accents on the ‘N’ logo and studded rubber outsole give the nod to the Statue of Liberty. On the sneaker’s lateral side panel, NB branding is joined by printed text that reads ‘We Need Leaders’ and ‘All Roads Lead Back to the Streets.’

results.name: Air Max 2090 SE GS 'Dark Purple Dust'
RS-Fast Caliente 'Taco Tuesday'
results.story: Inspired by taco trucks, the PUMA RS-Fast Caliente ‘Taco Tuesday’ applies a spicy red finish to the lifestyle runner, featuring an upper constructed from breathable textile with tonal leather overlays. Metallic silver detailing at the heel gives the nod to the foil wrapping typically used by taco trucks, while accompanying pull tabs are marked with ‘Pull to Open’ instructions. An embossed flame graphic on the tongue denotes extreme heat levels. In that same vein, the lateral heel is printed with text that reads ‘Keep Away from Eyes.’

results.name: Wmns Offcourt Duo Slide 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike women’s Offcourt Duo Slide ‘Black White’ delivers a premium take on the classic slide. The upper is composed of two black synthetic leather straps, both lined in 100% recycled fabric and the wider of the two stamped with a contrasting white Nike wordmark. A micro-texture on the Revive foam footbed is designed for non-slip comfort. A lightweight EVA outsole features a circular traction pattern for optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Skycourt 'Cream Lichen Rock'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Skycourt ‘Cream Lichen Rock’ features a subtle color palette inspired by springtime in Japan, executed on a retro build that takes its cues from the Gel Altitude volleyball shoe from 1990. The sneaker makes use of an ivory-colored twill upper with ASICS’ signature tiger stripes embroidered on the lateral quarter panel. A textured heel overlay in a pale green finish delivers a subtle pop of contrasting color. Anchoring the low-top is a rubber cupsole borrowed from the Japan S silhouette.

results.name: Future Rider Taqueria 'Taco Tuesday'
results.story: As its monikers suggests, the PUMA Future Rider Taqueria ‘Taco Tuesday’ draws inspiration from Mexican restaurants, carts and food trucks that specialize in tacos. The upper is constructed from white textile with tonal overlays in suede and cracked leather. Green, red and yellow accents signify various toppings, chilis and salsas, while ‘Cash Only’ is inscribed across the heels of the left and right shoe, emblematic of the payment policy that holds sway in many taquerias.

results.name: Chuck 70 High 'Breaking Down Barriers'
results.story: The Converse Chuck 70 High ‘Breaking Down Barriers’ celebrates the legacy of Indiana’s Crispus Attucks Tigers, who in 1955 became the first all-black high school basketball team to win a state championship. The high-top utilizes a white textile upper with four stars on the lateral heel, a symbolic nod to Crispus Attucks’ four state titles. The Tigers’ logo adorns the tongue, while the team’s yellow and green colors are applied to the rubber midsole and outsole.

results.name: Pro Leather High 'Breaking Down Barriers'
results.story: The Converse Pro Leather High ‘Breaking Down Barriers’ pays tribute to Indiana’s Crispus Attucks Tigers, who in 1955 became the first all-black high school basketball team to win a state championship. Inspired by the team’s letterman’s jacket, the vintage hoops shoe features a white felt upper with mismatched Star Chevron branding in yellow and green. The heel tab on the left shoe is embroidered with ‘CA 55,’ while the Tigers’ logo adorns the right. Four embroidered stars signify Crispus Attucks’ four state championships.

results.name: Wmns RS-Fast 'Safari'
results.story: The PUMA women’s RS-Fast ‘Safari’ dresses up the retro-inspired silhouette with varying shades of pink throughout a layered upper built with mesh, leather and no-sew synthetic skins. The pastel hues are joined by stylized animal prints on the breathable mesh tongue and molded TPU heel counter. PUMA’s signature Formstrip is relegated to a sculpted midsole built with cushy RS foam. A coral-tinged rubber outsole provides grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: Thundercats x RS-X 'T3CH - White Barbados Cherry'
results.story: The Thundercats x PUMA RS-X T3CH ‘White Barbados Cherry’ is drawn from a larger capsule collection inspired by the ‘80s animated television series. The lifestyle runner wears a white textile upper with a drawcord lacing system, tonal no-sew overlays and contrasting black and red accents throughout. Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of a polyurethane midsole, featuring a soft RS foam core and sculpted sidewalls fitted with geometric TPU pieces.

results.name: Flex Runner PS 'Crimson Bliss Metallic Platinum'
results.story: Constructed for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner PS ‘Crimson Bliss Metallic Platinum’ delivers a versatile silhouette that can be slipped easily on and off, thanks to a laceless mesh upper with webbing pull tabs at the tongue and heel. The sneaker’s warm coral hue is offset by a metallic silver Swoosh that adorns a supportive midfoot cage. The lightweight build is supported by a cushy foam sole unit, featuring flex grooves underfoot that promote a smooth, natural stride.

results.name: Wmns Blazer Low '77 'Triple White'
results.story: The Nike women’s Blazer Low ‘77 ‘Triple White’ treats the vintage hoops shoe to a pristine blank-slate finish. The upper is constructed from crisp white leather and branded with a matching white retro Swoosh, along with an embossed Nike wordmark on the heel tab. The tonal theme continues on a woven tag atop a vintage exposed-foam tongue. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a classic herringbone traction pattern originally designed for the hardwood.

results.name: adidas GT Paris SNS
results.story: Releasing as part of the Swedish retailer’s ‘Hometown Love’ series, the Sneakersnstuff x adidas GT ‘Paris’ features a familiar color scheme that pays homage to the City of Lights. The upper is constructed from ivory-colored suede with tonal leather three-stripes, a blue molded tongue and a red leather heel tab stamped with an adidas Trefoil. Additional adidas branding appears on a custom sockliner printed with a map of Paris. The low-profile silhouette rides on a semi-translucent gum rubber cupsole.

results.name: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Light Smoke Grey
Slam Jam x Bosey MC High 'Black'
results.story: Designed in collaboration with the Italian retailer, the Slam Jam x Converse Bosey MC High ‘Black’ reimagines the utilitarian silhouette with a street-ready aesthetic. The upper is constructed from Lurex ripstop nylon and reinforced with the Bosey’s signature rubber toe cap and foxing. Reflective details offer added visibility in low-light conditions, while a thermal lining provides insulated warmth. Underfoot, a lugged rubber outsole delivers optimal grip on rough terrain.

results.name: Canyon Sandal 'Cargo Khaki'
results.story: The Nike Canyon Sandal ‘Cargo Khaki’ projects an ACG-inspired aesthetic, highlighted by a rugged build finished in a contrasting blend of earth tones and vibrant accents. The upper utilizes triple-strap closure for a secure, custom fit, while a dual-density foam midsole offers lightweight cushioning with every step. The contoured outsole features deep flex grooves and a traction pattern modeled after Nike’s classic waffle tread. Rubber under the toe and heel provides added durability.

results.name: Wmns Lavante Terrain 'Black Ceramic Pink'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Lavante Terrain ‘Black Ceramic Pink’ highlights a simple two-tone finish on a versatile running shoe built to handle off-road use. Breathable black mesh on the upper is fortified with tonal synthetic leather overlays and accented with contrasting pink side stripes. Responsive cushioning arrives via a full-length FuelFoam midsole, supported by a high-traction rubber outsole that offers reliable grip through all conditions.

results.name: Zoom Blazer Mid SB 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike Zoom Blazer Mid SB ‘Black White’ floods the exterior of the retro silhouette with a stark one-note finish, save for the signature branding element that adorns each of the side panels. The sneaker’s retro Swoosh stands out in white suede against a pitch-black backdrop, also constructed from suede and embellished with tonal stitch detailing. Performance benefits include a springy Zoom Air unit in the sockliner and a grippy herringbone-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Slam Jam x Bosey MC Low 'Triple White'
results.story: The Slam Jam x Converse Bosey MC Low ‘Triple White’ treats the utilitarian silhouette to a clean, modern makeover. The Italian retailer dresses the low-top in Lurex ripstop nylon, secured with a looped lacing system and accented with hi-vis reflective binding. The Bosey’s signature rubber foxing and toe cap are joined by a durable rubber outsole equipped with outdoor lugs. Mismatched sockliners are embellished with Converse and Slam Jam branding.

results.name: Wmns Air Max Bella TR 4 'White Green Glow'
Killshot OG 'Sail Oil Green'
results.story: The Nike Killshot OG ‘Sail Oil Green’ showcases an elemental two-tone palette on a lifestyle silhouette modeled after the vintage tennis shoe from 1979. Equipped with the plush exposed-foam tongue of the original, the low-top carries a breathable off-white mesh upper with tonal suede overlays at the toe and heel. Contrasting olive green accents land on the retro leather Swoosh and Nike-branded heel tab. A durable rubber cupsole anchors the throwback silhouette.

results.name: Court Legacy Print 'Tie-Dye'
results.story: The Nike Court Legacy Print ‘Tie-Dye’ features slip-on construction on a low-top silhouette that channels vintage tennis style. A blue tie-dye print suffuses the breathable canvas upper, lined in synthetic leather and equipped with elastic gore panels for easy on and off. The sneaker rides on a vulcanized rubber midsole with pinstripe detailing and a Swoosh-branded license plate at the heel. Underfoot, a herringbone-tread gum rubber outsole provides optimal grip.

results.name: 1400 Made in USA 'White'
results.story: The New Balance 1400 Made in USA ‘White’ delivers a blank-canvas iteration of the retro runner originally released in 1994. The monotone finish that suffuses the white leather upper extends to every component of the shoe, including the sneaker’s interior and tooling. The latter comprises an ENCAP midsole, featuring a plush EVA core within a tough polyurethane carrier for added support and durability, along with a durable rubber outsole

results.name: Maison Margiela x Club C 'Black'
results.story: Crafted in partnership with the French luxury fashion house, the Maison Margiela x Reebok Club C ‘Black'’ updates the retro trainer with the former’s trompe-l’oeil design from the 1996 Spring/Summer collection. The low-top makes use of an upper constructed from a single piece of flat leather, finished in black and printed with a scanned image of the original Club C shoe. The result is a unique 2D optical illusion effect, complemented by signature Margiela flourishes that include stitched detailing on the heel tab and three orderly rows of numbers on the woven tongue tag.

results.name: Wmns Adilette Comfort Slide 'Legacy Purple'
results.story: The adidas women’s Adilette Comfort Slide ‘Legacy Purple’ updates the cushy sandal with an injected EVA midsole in a subtle violet hue. Step-in comfort is provided by the combination of a contoured footbed and a wide single-bandage upper, lined in quick-drying textile and marked with a repeating adidas logo. Underfoot, a durable synthetic outsole features a crisp white finish and a diamond traction pattern for reliable grip.

results.name: Jazz Court 'White Black'
results.story: The Saucony Jazz Court ‘White Black’ treats the vintage silhouette to an essential two-tone color scheme. The low-top’s white leather upper is accented with contrasting black detailing on the woven tongue tag, Saucony-branded heel tab and signature river logo on the quarter panel. A perforated toe box offers improved breathability, while an anti-microbial lining keeps feet feeling fresh. Underfoot, a herringbone-tread gum rubber outsole provides grippy traction.

results.name: adidas ZX 2K Phormar Craig Green White
results.story: The Craig Green x adidas ZX 2K Phormar ‘White’ combines the British fashion designer’s progressive sensibilities with adidas ZX running technology. One piece of semi-translucent white nylon is utilized on the upper, featuring high-density tension cords running through stitched channels outlining the collar, heel and throat. A drawcord lacing system works in tandem with an interior sleeve to provide a secure fit. Responsive cushioning comes courtesy of a partially wrapped Boost midsole, reinforced underfoot by a translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Jazz Court 'White Green'
results.story: The Saucony Jazz Court ‘White Green’ is clad in a standard white leather upper with forest green accents. They take the form of Saucony’s signature river logo, as well as a suede heel tab and woven tongue tag. An off-white rubber midsole enhances the shoe’s vintage aesthetic, while an encapsulated EVA foam wedge provides lightweight cushioning. A gum rubber outsole, complete with a pivot point and herringbone traction pattern, yields maximum grip.

results.name: Predator Accelerator FG 'Royal Blue Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas Predator Accelerator FG ‘Royal Blue Solar Yellow’ delivers an updated version of the shoe’s namesake model from 1998. Like its antecedent, the low-top is constructed from stitched K-leather with a traditional fold-over tongue, off-center lacing and rubber elements throughout the strike zone. Underfoot, the updated split Controlframe outsole is borrowed from the Predator Freak+, featuring studded traction designed for firm-ground surfaces.

results.name: Jordan 12 Retro Arctic Punch (TD)
results.story: Made for a new generation of Michael Jordan fans, the Air Jordan 12 Retro TD ‘Arctic Pink' presents a colorful take on the silhouette that MJ wore when he clinched his penultimate NBA championship in 1997. Hot pink coloring on the sneaker’s pull tab, collar lining and branding elements is rendered in a diluted shade throughout the distressed upper, resulting in an abstract pattern that’s offset by pristine white overlays in synthetic leather. A matching white foam sole unit offers lightweight cushioning for little feet.

results.name: Adizero Spark MD J 'Royal Blue'
results.story: The adidas Adizero Spark MD J ‘Royal Blue’ delivers a lightweight two-tone football cleat built for little kids. The streamlined upper is constructed from coated Sprintskin, emblazoned with three-stripe branding on the lateral toe. Breathable mesh is utilized on the padded collar and tongue. A low-profile Bounce midsole is supported by a molded Quickframe outsole, featuring an aggressive lug pattern for stop-and-go traction.

results.name: Adizero 11 Primeknit 'White Black'
results.story: The adidas Adizero 11 Primeknit ‘White Black’ outfits the performance football cleat in a breathable white knit upper, fortified with a durable TPU overlay and accented with contrasting black three-stripe branding. Dual webbing pull tabs and an elastic ankle cuff allow for easy on and off, while an integrated lacing system produces a feeling of lock-down. The seamless build is supported by a lightweight Sprintframe outsole, equipped with a series of Sprintstuds that deliver turf-digging traction through every play.

results.name: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Light Violet (GS)
results.story: Built for big kids, the Nike Blazer Mid ‘77 Suede GS ‘Light Violet’ makes over the retro silhouette with a monochromatic pastel finish throughout the suede upper. The pale lavender hue extends to the laces, retro leather Swoosh and Nike-branded heel tab. Contrasting colors are confined to the woven tongue tag, featuring a standard Nike wordmark and an orange Swoosh. The sneaker’s traditional autoclave tooling comes complete with a standard herringbone tread.

results.name: Superstar J 'Pink Iridescent'
results.story: Built for little kids, the adidas Superstar J ‘Pink Iridescent’ updates the shell-toed sneaker icon with an eye-catching finish. The pink leather upper is accented with serrated white leather three-stripes and multicolor iridescent paneling on the sneaker’s lateral side. A similar iridescent finish is applied to adidas branding hits on the tongue and heel tab. The low-top is mounted on a durable rubber cupsole, complete with a herringbone traction pattern underfoot.

results.name: Jordan 12 Retro Arctic Punch (GS)
results.story: Constructed for big kids, the Air Jordan 12 Retro GS ‘Arctic Pink’ updates the vintage mid-top with energetic pops of color. They take the form of hot pink detailing on the sneaker’s heel tab, molded eyelets and Jumpman tongue branding. A more diffuse shade of pink is spread out over the cracked suede upper to create an irregular, abstract pattern. The mid-top rides on a Phylon midsole, reinforced with a rigid shank plate and a herringbone rubber outsole underfoot.

results.name: Vapor Edge Elite 360 Flyknit 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike Vapor Edge Elite 360 Flyknit ‘Black White’ showcases a gradient finish on a football cleat engineered for lightweight speed. The sock-like upper is crafted from 360-degree Flyknit and overlaid with protective NikeSkin. A toggle ghost lacing system provides a secure fit, while an elastic cuff combines with a webbing pull tab to deliver easy on and off. An internal full-length plate yields flexible support. Underfoot, widely placed studs offer superior grip.

results.name: React Vision '3M Pack' By You
results.story: Created via the brand’s customization service, the Nike React Vision ‘3M Pack’ By You carries a textile upper lined in Thinsulate. Reflective Scotchlite detailing on the sneaker’s no-sew heel overlay and distinctive patchwork eyestays offer added visibility in low-light conditions. A woven 3M tag on the heel of the right shoe can be left intact or torn away. The sneaker rides on a plush React foam midsole, reinforced underfoot with rubber pods for enhanced durability and traction.

results.name: Nike Air Max 97 Leopard (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Air Max 97 ‘Leopard’ features a unique design that blends twin inspirations drawn from the natural world. In addition to the sneaker’s wavy overlays, treated to a reflective finish and designed to mimic a water ripple effect, the textile and suede upper is covered in an all-over graphic made up of numerous leopard spots. Mini Swooshes in Peach Cream offer contrasting pops of color. The sneaker is mounted on a polyurethane midsole with full-length Max Air cushioning.

results.name: Basket Profi 'Mesa'
results.story: The adidas Basket Profi ‘Mesa’ updates the vintage hoops shoe with a stitched textile upper in a light brown hue. Tonal serrated three-stripes are joined by a circular adidas badge on the lateral ankle. A drawcord lacing system provides a secure fit, while a suede heel overlay offers added durability and support. The mid-top is mounted on a contrasting black rubber cupsole, featuring a grippy herringbone traction pattern underfoot.

results.name: Swift Run X J 'Black Fluorescent Pop'
results.story: Built for little kids, the adidas Swift Run X J ‘Black Fluorescent Pop’ treats the retro-inspired low-top to an essential black and white color scheme, enlivened with fluorescent pops of color on the eyelets and forefoot. An Ortholite sockliner combines with an EVA midsole to deliver soft cushioning with each step. Underfoot, a black rubber outsole is equipped with a series of flex grooves that accommodate the natural motion of the foot.

results.name: Pro Model 'White Gold Metallic'
results.story: The adidas Pro Model ‘White Gold Metallic’ gives the vintage hoops shoe a pristine makeover, featuring a white leather upper with gilded branding hits. They include ‘Pro Model’ stamped on the lateral quarter panel and adidas’ Trefoil logo on the navy heel tab. The latter hue is repeated on the collar lining and rubber outsole, equipped with a traditional herringbone tread for reliable traction. Heritage details include the iconic rubber shell toe and serrated leather three-stripes.

results.name: Air Zoom Victory Tour 2 'White Metallic Platinum'
results.story: The Nike Air Zoom Victory Tour 2 ‘White Metallic Platinum’ makes use of a one-piece full-grain leather upper, treated to a water-proof coating and equipped with a foam padded collar. Responsive cushioning arrives via a Zoom Air unit stitched directly to the upper, supported by a full-length plate for improved energy return. Nike React foam under the heel adds to the shoe’s cushioned comfort. The hybrid outsole combines integrated traction with seven removable spikes for exceptional grip.

results.name: Wmns Superstar Boot 'Night Indigo'
results.story: The adidas women’s Superstar Boot ‘Night Indigo’ reimagines the vintage hoops shoe as a rugged outdoor boot. The monochromatic navy upper is constructed from lightweight nylon with tonal suede paneling at the heel and toe, the latter embellished with stitched lines that replicate the iconic shell toe of the original. The sneaker-boot hybrid is mounted on a black rubber sole unit, featuring a herringbone traction pattern for maximum grip.

results.name: adidas ZX 2K Phormar Craig Green Blue
results.story: The Craig Green x adidas ZX 2K Phormar ‘Blue’ brings the British fashion designer’s unrestrained aesthetic to the Three Stripes’ ZX running franchise. An exposed tension cord system adds structure to an upper built with semi-translucent nylon in a bold royal blue finish. A drawcord lacing system combines with a stretchy interior sleeve to deliver a snug, comfortable fit. The lightweight sneaker rides on a full-length Boost midsole, painted black and partially enclosed within a wraparound TPU cage.

results.name: Terrex Speed Pro Trail 'White Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas Terrex Speed Pro Trail ‘White Solar Yellow’ carries a streamlined build that blends visibility and sustainability. Recycled materials are incorporated into a neon-tinged mesh upper, overlaid with abrasion-resistant overlays and accented with 3M reflective detailing. The low-top rides on a full-length Lightstrike midsole, marked with Terrex branding and finished in a black and white gradient finish. A lugged Continental rubber outsole provides sure footing on uneven terrain.

results.name: Revolution 5 SE PS 'Crimson Tint Multi'
results.story: The Nike Revolution 5 SE PS ‘Crimson Tint Multi’ highlights a pastel finish on a versatile sneaker designed for little kids. Elastic no-tie laces combine with a webbing pull tab and an adjustable hook-and-loop strap to provide easy on and off. The upper, constructed from peach-colored knit textile and accented with a color-fade Swoosh, rides on a plush foam midsole. Underfoot, a full-length rubber outsole in Glacier Blue offers durable traction.

results.name: MD Valiant GS 'White Multi'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike MD Valiant GS ‘White Multi’ highlights a limited spectrum of pastel accents on a casual sneaker inspired by ‘80s running style. The upper is constructed from white textile with tonal synthetic leather overlays at the toe and heel. The signature Swoosh is rendered in a gradient blend of yellow, blue and pink hues, a color combination that’s repeated on the Nike logo that adorns the iridescent heel tab. A waffle-traction rubber outsole delivers an additional nod to Nike heritage.

results.name: Adizero 11 Primeknit 'White Clear Grey'
results.story: The adidas Adizero 11 Primeknit ‘White Clear Grey’ delivers a blank-slate colorway of a lightweight football cleat built for speed on the gridiron. The upper is constructed from breathable white Primeknit, bolstered with a tonal TPU overlay for added support and durability. An elastic cuff is equipped with dual webbing pull tabs to assist with easy on and off. A Sprintframe outsole features a reinforced heel and strategically placed Sprintstuds for stop-and-go traction.

results.name: adidas Nizza Lo Wales Bonner Purple
